node.text:
On his first day of retirement, @DrewBrees and his wife Brittany visited some places with special meaning for them around the city, including Tom Benson's gravesite.
 
Mrs. Benson joined them on the visit.
 
Mr. Benson passed away three years ago today 🙏

node.text: During the pandemic, Nicole Fitzgerald fed many families who didn’t have access to food regularly. The Saints and @waitrapp teamed up to recognize her for her generosity, gifting her with a $250 credit delivered by Gumbo, himself! Thank you, Nicole, for all you’ve done for our community over the past year and beyond.
